### Product Management Tests
### Test CRUD operations cho products

@token = {{loginAdmin.response.body.accessToken}}
@categoryId = {{createParentCategory.response.body.id}}

### 1. List All Products (Public)
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products?page=1&pageSize=20

### 2. Search Products
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products?search=iphone&page=1&pageSize=10

### 3. Filter by Category
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products?categorySlug=dien-thoai&page=1&pageSize=10

### 4. Filter by Price Range
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products?minPriceInt=10000000&maxPriceInt=30000000&page=1&pageSize=10

### 5. Create Product
# @name createProduct
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "IP14-PRO-256-BLK",
  "name": "iPhone 14 Pro 256GB",
  "slug": "iphone-14-pro-256gb",
  "priceInt": 2999000000,
  "stock": 50,
  "description": "iPhone 14 Pro với chip A16 Bionic mạnh mẽ",
  "imageUrls": [
    "https://example.com/iphone-14-pro-1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/iphone-14-pro-2.jpg"
  ],
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "attributes": {
    "color": "Đen",
    "storage": "256GB",
    "ram": "6GB"
  },
  "model3dUrl": "https://example.com/models/iphone-14-pro.glb"
}

### 6. Create Second Product
# @name createProduct2
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "SS-S23-128-WHT",
  "name": "Samsung Galaxy S23 128GB",
  "slug": "samsung-galaxy-s23-128gb",
  "priceInt": 1899000000,
  "stock": 30,
  "description": "Samsung Galaxy S23 với màn hình AMOLED",
  "imageUrls": [
    "https://example.com/samsung-s23-1.jpg"
  ],
  "categoryId": "{{categoryId}}",
  "attributes": {
    "color": "Trắng",
    "storage": "128GB"
  }
}

### 7. Get Product by ID
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products/{{createProduct.response.body.id}}

### 8. Get Product by Slug
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/products/slug/iphone-14-pro-256gb

### 9. Update Product
PUT {{gatewayUrl}}/products/{{createProduct.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priceInt": 2799000000,
  "stock": 45,
  "description": "iPhone 14 Pro - Giảm giá đặc biệt!"
}

### 10. Delete Product
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/products/{{createProduct2.response.body.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Try to create duplicate SKU (expect 409)
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "IP14-PRO-256-BLK",
  "name": "Duplicate Product",
  "slug": "duplicate-product",
  "priceInt": 1000000
}